nt month. Days with available slots are marked with a \",[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"green underline\"}],\". The client clicks a date to see the available time slots for that day, then taps a green slot to reserve it.\"]}]\n34:[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":[\"A \",[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Summary\"}],\" panel on the right shows the selected service, agent, and total price. The client can also click \",[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"+ Add More\"}],\" to add additional services to the same booking.\"]}]\n35:[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\",\"id\":\"step-5--enter-contact-details\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"data-card\":\"\",\"href\":\"#step-5--enter-contact-details\",\"className\":\"peer\",\"children\":\"Step 5 — Enter contact details\"}],[\"$\",\"$L1c\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":\"$d:props:children:3:props:children:12:props:children:1:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\",\"aria-hidden\":true}]]}]\n36:[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"The client fills in their information:\"}]\n37:[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"children\":[\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"New Client\"}],\" — enters their details for the first time\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Existing Client\"}],\" — enters their registered phone number to pull up their profile\"]}],\"\\n\"]}]\n38:[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":[\"They can also add any \",[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"special requests or notes\"}],\" in the Additional Comments field.\"]}]\n39:[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\",\"id\":\"step-6--appointment-confirmed\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"data-card\":\"\",\"href\":\"#step-6--appointment-confirmed\",\"className\":\"peer\",\"child